---

## 2 Color Guidelines

## Type HEX Usage

Primary Orange #EB6424 Buttons, icons, highlighted text
Secondary Green #89AC46 Success states, tags
Light Orange Bg #FA9500 Hover background or accents
Cream Page Bg #FEF3E2 Main page background
Gray Text #A0A0A0 Secondary text

Tip: Highlight text with primary orange. Ensure contrast with background.

---

3. Links

---

Internal page:
<a href="/pages/main.html">Go to Main Page</a>

External link:
<a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">External Site</a>

Navbar or button navigation should use window.location.href or <a> tags.

---

4. Images & Icons

---

Icons: Use SVG for scalability and color control.
Image sizes:

- Header icons: 24x24 or 18x18 (Mobile)
- Content images: maintain aspect ratio, responsive

---

5. Page Element Links

---

## Page Component/Element Link/Path

Main page Back button /pages/main.html
Favorites Navbar Favorites /pages/favorites.html
Profile Navbar Profile /pages/profile.html
Restaurant Favorite Heart Button Layout only, no interaction yet

---

6. Component Naming

---

JS components in /src/components/
Use PascalCase filenames, e.g.:
Navbar.js
BackButton.js
RestaurantHeader.js
Each component exports a function:
export function ComponentName() { ... }

---

7. Tailwind Style Conventions

---

Button: rounded-full bg-[#FEF3E2] text-[#EB6424] shadow border border-black/10
Hover: hover:bg-[#EB6424] hover:text-[#FEF3E2] transition-colors duration-200
Text: text-[#A0A0A0] font-medium text-sm md:text-base
Flex layout: flex items-center justify-center gap-2
